<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>OTP Verification</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f7f7f7;
        color: #333;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      h1 {
        color: #007bff;
        text-align: center;
      }
      p {
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .otp {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-align: center;
        margin: 20px 0;
        padding: 15px;
        background-color: #f0f0f0;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>OTP Verification</h1>
      <p>Dear User,</p>
      <p>Thank you for signing up with our service. Please use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to verify your account:</p>
      <div class="otp">{{ otp }}</div>
      <p>This OTP is valid for a limited time only. If you did not initiate this request, please ignore this email.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>Bot V2 Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
